HEADWORD: Geastrum
<hw>Geastrum</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The type genus of the
<fam>Geastraceae</fam>, consisting of fungi whose outer peridium when
dry splits into starlike segments.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Geastrum</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
